ft stellar assembly provides a powerful testbed\nfor WDM models, accessible with the upcoming JWST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Aug 2014 20:05:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 May 2015 09:45:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
