ria are necessary\nto accurately determine the effects of gravitationally induced decoherence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 2014 06:53:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2014 18:19:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 28 Jun 2015 14:53:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-30"}
